"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp;求婚招数</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：模仿电影阿甘正传求婚</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阿甘正传中，阿甘向珍妮求婚时说的这句话让人泪崩。珍妮和阿甘原是青梅竹马的一对，他俩却是如此的迥然不同</span>;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阿甘不抽烟不喝酒，只是喜欢喝上“一点点”汽水，他谦虚忍让、诚恳善良，只会默默付出，不曾要过回报，他勇敢地冒死拯救战友，他乐善好施、知恩图报</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">而珍妮喝酒吸烟，甚至吸毒性乱，她狂乱不羁、放纵堕落，她成天幻想成为明星，追逐自己所谓的梦想</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">她一次次冷酷回绝阿甘，又一次次伤透阿甘的心。阿甘生活在那个令人向往的纯真世界中，而珍妮却生活在满是诱惑的沉迷世界里。他们是如此的对立，是两个生活在完完全全不同世界里的人。但是阿甘认定了，珍妮就是他生命中的那个女孩，任何事情都无法改变这个事实，即使是死亡。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp;&nbsp;求婚招数</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">二</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：发动群众，共襄盛举，群策群力之下最终赢得美人芳心</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　一天晚上，和以往一样，王小姐和几个牌友打完牌后走回自家楼下大堂。她发现，平时灯火通明的大堂今晚竟漆黑一片，这时，抒情浪漫的英文情歌响起来，一个用红色灯管串起的</span>“<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">I LOVE YOU</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">”，在黑暗中显得特别耀眼。她正纳闷间，大堂的灯忽然亮起来。王小姐惊讶地发现，不知道什么时候眼前竟站着她的男朋友张先生，手里捧着一束玫瑰。而已经离开的几个牌友，也不知道什么时候折了回来。“埋伏”在走火通道里的几个朋友，鼓着掌一下涌到她面前。王小姐既惊讶又激动，此时，张先生递上钻戒和玫瑰花。大家屏气凝神，等待王小姐的反应。王小姐羞涩地接过了玫瑰，伸出手让男朋友为她戴上了戒指。大家激动地欢呼起来……</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　求婚招数三：确定最佳求婚日</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">经历种种磨难，你终于可以大声向她求婚了，可时间又是一个问题，到底该选择哪一天呢</span>?<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">首先，你肯定不希望在她最忙碌的日子提出求婚请求，所以在行动前请先仔 细查看她近期的行程表，了解一下她最近是否有大型工作项目临近截止期限</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">或是最近她是否需要参加重要的活动或聚会</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">?</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">总之要确保求婚的日期不和其它重要事件起冲突，以免另她陷入两难的境地。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　求婚招数</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">四</span></span><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">：事先写好求婚爱语</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　相信每个女人都会因为听到男方想与她共度今生的甜蜜理由而感动不已。所以，在说出那句重要的话之前，你可以事先想好一些特别而真诚的爱她的理由。因为，在这样的重要时刻，有可能兴奋的心情会让你迫不及待，紧张的情绪会令你语无伦次，有很多男人甚至会忘记说出至关重要</span>“嫁给我，好吗”这句话，而另外一些男人则是因为满脑子都盘旋着这句话而忘记其它一切想说的话。所以，事先反复练习很有必要，想感动她就别偷懒<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">!</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　做好求婚前保密工作</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　把求婚计划告诉越多的人就意味着越难保守秘密。所以，在你召集亲友帮忙之前，可是要仔细斟酌备选名单哦</span>!<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">尽可能地确保他们不会因为过于兴奋而走漏风声，破坏你精心计划的甜蜜惊喜。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(138,27,0,'用简单浪漫的英文诗句 助你秀出爱情','','','qiuhuning',2,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2015-06-23 16:45:56','Addy','','',1,1,'现在许多男生向心仪的对象表白时，都想写上一首浪漫的情书，这样才能够更显得自己的能力和真情，那么浪漫的“英文”爱情诗句要怎么写呢?今天小编为你献上最经典的浪漫英文情诗88句，希望能够帮你表白成功吧！',0,'<p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:30px\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201610/14766967074118.png\" title=\"用简单浪漫的英文诗句 助你秀出爱情.png\" alt=\"用简单浪漫的英文诗句 助你秀出爱情.png\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　1、　&quot;whatever our soulsare made of, his and mine are the same.&quot;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　《呼啸山庄》</span>“不论我们的灵魂是什么做成的，他的和我的是一模一样的。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　2、&quot;But soft! What lightthrough yonder window breaks? It is the east and Juliet is the sun&quot;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　《罗密欧与朱丽叶》</span>“嘘!那边窗户里亮起的是什么光?哦，那是东方，朱丽叶就是太阳!”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　3、&quot;He was my North, mySouth, my East and West, My working week and my Sunday rest,My noon, mymidnight, my talk, my song; I thought that love would last forever: I waswrong”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　《四个婚礼一个葬礼》</span>“他是我的南北，我的西东。是我作息的意义。是我的日夜，欢唱谈话的内容。我以为爱会永恒不朽..…我错了。”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　4、Grow old along with me! Thebest is yet to be&quot;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　罗伯特</span>·布朗宁：一和我一起慢慢变老吧!最好的日子还在后头。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　5、&quot;For you see, each dayI love you more. Today more than yesterday and less than tomorrow”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　罗斯蒙德</span>·杰拉德：你知道吗?我每天都爱你更多。今天爱的比昨天多，明天爱的比今夭多。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　6、&quot;If you live to be ahundred, I want to live to be a hundred minus one day so I never have to livewithout you”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　米尔恩</span>:假如你的寿命是100年，那我希望自己活到100岁的前一天，因为那样我的生命中每天都有你。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　7、With love, you should goahead and take the risk of getting hurt, because love is an amazing feeling.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　布兰妮</span>.斯皮尔斯：恋爱的时候就应该无所畏惧、勇往直前，因为爱情就是如此妙不可言。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　8、I love you not because of who you are,but because of who I am when I am with you.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　我爱你，不是因为你是一个怎样的人，而是因为我喜欢与你在一起时的感觉。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　9、No man or woman is worth your tears,and the one who is ,won&#39;t make you cry.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　没有人值得你流泪，值得让你这么做的人不会让你哭泣。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:30px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　10、The worst way to miss someone is to be sitting right beside them knowing you can&#39;t have them.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　失去某人，最糟糕的莫过于，他近在身旁，却犹如远在天边。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　11、Never frown,even when you are sad,because you never know who is falling in love with your smile.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　纵然伤心，也不要悉眉不展，因为你不知是谁会爱上你的笑容。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　12、To the world you may be one person,but to one person you may be the world.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　对于世界而言，你是一个人</span>;但是对于某人，你是他的整个世界。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　13、Don&#39;t waste your time on a man/woman,who isn&#39;t willing to waste their time on you.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　不要为那些不愿在你身上花费时间的人而浪费你的时间。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　14、Just because someone doesn&#39;t love you the way you want them to,doesn&#39;t mean they don&#39;t love you with all they have.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　爱你的人如果没有按你所希望的方式爱你，那并不代表他们没有全心全意地爱你。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　15、Don&#39;t try to hard,the best things come when you least expect them to.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　不要着急，最好的总会在最不经意的时候出现。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　16、Maybe God wants us to meet a few wrong people before meeting the right one,so that when we finally meet the person,we will know how to be grateful.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　在遇到梦中人之前，上天也许会安排我们先遇到别人</span>;在我们终于遇见心仪的人时，便应当心存感激。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　17、Don&#39;t cry because it is over,smile because it happened.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　不要因为结束而哭泣，微笑吧，为你的曾经拥有。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　18、Where there is great love, there are always miracles.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　哪里有真爱存在，哪里就有奇迹。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　19、Love is like a butterfly. It goes where it pleases and it pleases where it goes.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　爱情就像一只蝴蝶，它喜欢飞到哪里，就把欢乐带到哪里。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:30px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　20、If I had a single flower for every time I think about you, I could walk forever in my garden.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　假如每次想起你我都会得到一朵鲜花，那么我将永远在花丛中徜徉。</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　21、Within you I lose myself, without you I find myself wanting to be lost again.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　有了你，我迷失了自我。失去你，我多么希望自己再度迷失。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　22、At the touch of love everyone becomes a poet.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　每一个沐浴在爱河中的人都是诗人。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　23、Look into my eyes - you will see what you mean to me.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　看看我的眼睛，你会发现你对我而言意味着什么。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　24、Distance makes the hearts grow fonder.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　距离使两颗心靠得更近。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　25、I need him like I need the air to breathe.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　我需要他，正如我需要呼吸空气。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　26、If equal affection cannot be, let the more loving be me.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　如果没有相等的爱，那就让我爱多一些吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　27、Love is a vine that grows into our hearts.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　爱是长在我们心里的藤蔓。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　28、If I know what love is, it is because of you.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　因为你，我懂得了爱。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　29、Love is the greatest refreshment in life.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　爱情是生活最好的提神剂。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:30px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　30、Love never dies.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　爱情永不死。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　31、The darkness is no darkness with thee.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　有了你，黑暗不再是黑暗。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　32、We cease loving ourselves if no one loves us.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　如果没有人爱我们，我们也就不会再爱自己了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　33、There is no remedy for love but to love more.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　治疗爱的创伤唯有加倍地去爱。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　34、When love is not madness, it is not love.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　如果爱不疯狂就不是爱了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　35、A heart that loves is always young.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　有爱的心永远年轻。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　36、Love is blind.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　爱情是盲目的。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201610/14766967247135.png\" title=\"用简单浪漫的英文诗句 助你秀出爱情.png\" alt=\"用简单浪漫的英文诗句 助你秀出爱情.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　37、Love is like the moon, when it does not increase, it decreases.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　爱情就像月亮，不增则减。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　38、The soul cannot live without love.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　灵魂不能没有爱而存在。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　39、Brief is life, but love is long.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　生命虽短，爱却绵长。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:30px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　40、Who travels for love finds a thousand miles not longer than one.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　在爱人眼里，一千里的旅程不过一里。</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　41、Love keeps the cold out better than a cloak.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　爱比大衣更能驱走寒冷。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　42、Take away love, and our earth is a tomb.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　没有了爱，地球便成了坟墓。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　43、My heart is with you.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　我的爱与你同在。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　44、I miss you so much already and I haven&#39;t even left yet!</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　尽管还不曾离开，我已对你朝思暮想</span>!</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　45、I&#39;ll think of you every step of the way.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　我会想你，在漫漫长路的每一步。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　46、Wherever you go, whatever you do, I will be right here waiting for you.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　无论你身在何处，无论你为何忙碌，我都会在此守候。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201610/14766967394548.png\" title=\"用简单浪漫的英文诗句 助你秀出爱情.png\" alt=\"用简单浪漫的英文诗句 助你秀出爱情.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　47、Passionate love is a quenchless thirst.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　热烈的爱情是不可抑制的渴望。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　48、The most precious possession that ever comes to a man in this world is a woman&#39;s heart.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　在这个世界上，男人最珍贵的财产就是一个女人的心。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　49、One word frees us of all the weight and pain in life.That word is love.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Microsoft YaHei\">　　有一个词可以让我们摆脱生活中所有的负担和痛苦，那就是</span>&quot;爱情&quot;。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　50、Every day without you is like a book without pages.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　没有你的日子就像一本没有书页的书。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:30px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　51、Love is hard to get into, but harder to get out of.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　爱很难投入，但一旦投入，便更难走出。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　52、Love is a light that never dims.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　爱是一盏永不昏暗的明灯。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　53、May your love soar on the wings of a dove in flight.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　愿你的爱乘着飞翔的白鸽，展翅高飞。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　54、She who has never loved, has never lived.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　人活着总要爱一回。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　55、Life is the flower for which love is the honey.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　生命如花，爱情是蜜。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　56、No words are necessary between two loving hearts.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\">　　两颗相爱的心之间不需要言语。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;color: 