an></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">最著名的快闪案例肯定是</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">由</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">FOX频道打造的快闪求婚栏目《最幸福的女人》，现场群众演员和舞蹈演员达到几千名，通过环环相扣的情节，差点让女主角窒息，现场求婚活动视频上传到网路上后，几十分钟就达到上万次的点击，看完视频后，女生留言，有这样的求婚，我此生无憾，看完的难受留言说，让我的求婚仪式汗颜。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">（求婚总动员.浪漫策划师Rachael为您呈现）</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">案例二：</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">Tony</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">告诉女友</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">Lucy</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，下班后到两人第一次约会的艺术馆参观。当</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">Lucy</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">下班后和男友走在通往艺术馆的路上时，令她又惊又喜的一幕出现了：不断有陌生人上前，带着灿烂的笑容递给她一枝花。起初不明所以的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">Lucy</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">不愿接受，但很快，她手中全都是粉色和白色的美丽花朵。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">在到达艺术馆门口后，更加令人意想不到的情形出现了：刚才给</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">Lucy</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">鲜花的数十名陌生人都围坐在一起。随着现场的乐队奏起音乐，男友</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">Tony</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">身穿燕尾服单膝跪地，向</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">Lucy</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚，激动不已的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">Lucy</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">也答应了男友的请求。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">Tony</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">说，求婚成功多亏了这个疯狂的计划，</span>“在求婚这个重大时刻有这么多人支持我，与家人、朋友甚至陌生人分享求婚成功的喜悦，对我来说是一份天赐的礼物。”</span></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','',0,'','',0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(165,27,0,'浪漫唯美的创意求婚方式','','','qiuhuning',2,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2016-11-15 15:00:12','Addy','','/upload/images/201611/1479390594972.jpg',1,1,'想要像女生求婚。求婚创意很重要，女生都很喜欢唯美的场景，比如海滩，电影院等等。下面小编就带你一起去看看适合求婚的浪漫唯美的场地！',0,'<p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:29px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">做浪漫主角</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:29px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">　　这是一个充满着</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时尚元素</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的时代，我们</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">每一</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Verdana;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\"><sp