 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，当女主角被我们的工作人员引导到浪漫包房，接下来就开始观看男主</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">角</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">为她准备的表白视频，视频观看结束的时候，超萌公仔人偶出现在包房门口，此时的女主角还</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">以为玩偶里面是工作人员</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14797851063578.jpg\" title=\"男友化身公仔求婚，女主差点认不出.jpg\" alt=\"男友化身公仔求婚，女主差点认不出.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">　　当</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">男主扮演的玩偶</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">把手中的玫瑰花和</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">戒指</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">送到女主角的手里，并</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">喊出</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">他对她最亲密的称呼的时候，女主角瞬间</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">显得非常惊喜</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，把头套拿下的那一刻，女主角</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">更是惊喜的不得了</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。原来男主如此用心地为自己准备了眼前这一切，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">此刻，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">她觉得自己就是这个世界上最幸福的女生。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">KTV</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">包房里的每个细节都体现着男主满满的爱。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\"><br/></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14797851281640.jpg\" title=\"男友化身公仔求婚，女主差点认不出.jpg\" alt=\"男友化身公仔求婚，女主差点认不出.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">　　</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">KTV</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚适合那种不喜欢高调，不太喜欢热闹的女生。在</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">包房里</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚你们可以享受二人世界，享受这幸福美好的时刻。</span></span><br/></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(227,21,0,'无锡梁鸿国家湿地公园羡煞旁人的唯美求婚','','','Rachel',3,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2016-11-28 15:56:14','Rachel','','/upload/images/201611/14803198181458.jpg',1,1,'白马，鲜花，蜡烛，最唯美的星空灯架，一条属于我们的爱情长跑之路，当你看见这些的时候我看见了你眼中激动地泪水，我也知道呆呆傻傻的你只愿在我面前哭泣，所以亲爱的我们一辈子好好幸福下去...',0,'<p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">曾记得</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">她边想边甜蜜的说到：</span>“我以为你可以骑着白龙马来接我</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">云游九州</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span>”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14803198181458.jpg\" title=\"无锡梁鸿国家湿地公园羡煞旁人的唯美求婚.jpg\" alt=\"无锡梁鸿国家湿地公园羡煞旁人的唯美求婚.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">我淡淡的笑了，心想这个傻姑娘，这么</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">科幻</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的浪漫她也想得出来，真是傻的可爱。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">回想大一时她给了我一封信说她喜欢我时，我便笑了，这年头谁还写情书呀</span>!之后的相处中才知道她就是这么一个呆萌呆萌的女</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">孩</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，在她的身边我就有着想要给予她保护和依靠，这个世界上美女那么多但却没有一个向她这么单纯的人，单纯到大二时她生日我在寝室给她准备了惊喜骗她说我生病了，她立马找寝室的同学借钱急急冲冲的跑到我们宿舍拉着我的手要带我去医院去忽视了房间的布置和大大的蛋糕，到最后知道是恶作剧给她的惊喜</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">她</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">也是傻傻一笑。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">这么多年习惯了逗她想和她一起好好地一辈子在一起，也是时候我该向她求婚了，在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚总动员</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">公司的帮助下，我的求婚将在</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">无锡梁鸿国家湿地公园</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">展开，我的小呆萌你准备好接招了吗</span>?</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">白马，鲜花，蜡烛，最唯美的星空灯架，一条属于我们的爱情长跑之路，当你看见这些的时候我看见了你眼中激动地泪水，我也知道呆呆傻傻的你只愿在我面前哭泣，所以亲爱的我们一辈子好好幸福下去。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">白先生求婚感言：</span>“这场求婚我想了盼了半年，因为很多事情耽搁了一直没有去实现它，今天感谢</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软