/></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">出院后的一星期，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">男主</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">拿着</span>99朵玫瑰来到医院向</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">女主</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">表示爱情，他们的恋情很快就被双方父母所知道，而女</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">主</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的家人不愿意他们在一起，因为他们觉得双方年纪还太小不适合谈恋爱，但是父母的阻拦也抵不住他们</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">对</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">美好爱情的向往，两颗心越走越近，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">女主</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">说：</span>“你要是有着翅膀可以飞翔多好，就可以带着我远离这个地方，我们一起翱翔</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">看遍世界的美景。</span>”</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">男主</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">说：</span>“总有一天我会带着你一起远离这里，等我有了能力我要带你一起</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">云游四海</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">看遍</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">世界的美景。</span>”</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">毕业的他毅然放弃父母找的好工作选择创业，只为能给她幸福的生活，如今作为一家金融公司的老板，他们权财两得，想着是时候该向爱的她求婚了，在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚总动员</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">公司的倾力帮助下，一场唯美浪漫的求婚即将在他们身上展开。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14801727546425.jpg\" title=\"天津直升机浪漫求婚 带你翱翔世界.jpg\" alt=\"天津直升机浪漫求婚 带你翱翔世界.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">　　一架专属于他们俩的直升飞机带着两个幸福的人儿翱翔在天边看着地下的美景，而空旷的广场上有上万朵玫瑰组成的</span>“</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">xxx</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，我爱你</span>”从天空之中往下看唯美而又不失浪漫，我们的女主人公真的幸福得像花儿一样美。</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">男主</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">感言：感谢</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚总动员</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划公司的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">浪漫</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">策划师们</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">精心策划</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">与安排</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，我终于带着心爱的女人翱翔，今天是我此生中最幸福的一天，再次感谢。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',83,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(217,21,0,'大理别院浪漫求婚','','','Rachel',3,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2016-11-26 23:13:10','Rachel','','/upload/images/201611/14801735806999.png',1,1,'我们从首尔走到大理，让苍山和洱海见证我们的爱情，亲爱的...',0,'<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14801732541585.jpg\" title=\"大理别院浪漫求婚.jpg\" alt=\"大理别院浪漫求婚.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">他说：</span>“我们是在韩国留学时相遇的，我是</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">柳州</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">人，她是</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">大理</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">人，由于她在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">大理</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">长大，所以我追随她来到了</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">荆州</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，选择在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">大理</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">生活，今天是</span>201</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">6</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">年</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">8</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">月</span>1日，我想做关于一辈子的事，那就是</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">向</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">我的爱人求婚。</span>”韩语：“亲爱的，我爱你，现在正是时候了。”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14801733864279.jpg\" title=\"大理别院浪漫求婚.jpg\" alt=\"大理别院浪漫求婚.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">10点30分男女主角到达酒店入住</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">210</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">房间，此时女主并不知道此次计划，男主和策划人员通过短信交流，这是一个惊喜，为避免女主起疑心，策划人员假装自己求婚，进行现场布置。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14801734894683.png\" title=\"大理别院浪漫求婚.jpg\" alt=\"大理别院浪漫求婚.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">工作人员将钢琴搬到</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">洱</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">海边，用灯串做成心形灯海，气球上印着</span>“will you marry me”的字样，红色的路引，女主正在熟睡，男主悄悄下楼布置。和女主的妈妈自己的妈妈见面，男主悄悄进行最后的布置，一切准备OK男主叫女主下楼，开门片刻女主便发现墙上用韩文写着的路引，以及蜡烛气球摆设的路引，来到一楼，工作人员形成路引人手送上一只玫瑰，女主走到男主面前，男主说：“我们从首尔走到</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">大理</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，让苍山和洱海见证我们的爱情，亲爱的，我是多么的爱你，你知道我的心</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">意</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">!嫁给我好吗?我爱你，嫁给我吧。”女主接过玫瑰，拥抱接吻，此刻妈妈从角落出来为儿女送上祝福，女主感动万分，男主的妈妈也出现为女主送上祝福以礼物，女主说：“谢谢今天大家来捧场，也谢谢两位妈妈来支持，老公我爱你。”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14801735806999.png\" title=\"大理别院浪漫求婚.jpg\" alt=\"大理别院浪漫求婚.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">男主说：</span>“此时此刻</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">是我们此生</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">最重要的一</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刻</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">不仅感谢两位母亲的祝福，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">也再次感谢</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚总动员</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">公司给我们带来</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">精心策划的浪漫</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">惊喜求婚，我这辈子，不仅仅是这辈子，下辈子，下下辈子我都要好好爱她。</span>”</span></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(218,27,0,'浪漫求婚方案6例','','','Rachel',3,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2016-11-26 23:24:00','Rachel','','',1,1,'想要有一个浪漫的求婚方式，那便少不了一枚浪漫的求婚戒指...',0,'<p><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">一</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">、童话般的旋木求婚</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">如果女友是个有童心的人，你可以带她到游乐场，你们一起坐旋转木马，趁女友玩得开心时你突然消失，在她着急地找你时，灯光亮了，你捧着鲜花出现，单膝跪地，请求她嫁给你。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">二</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">、求婚戒指</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">想要有一个浪漫的求婚方式，那便少不了一枚浪漫的求婚戒指。如果要选择情侣之间最有意义的求婚戒指，求婚就是要让女孩子能够明白你可以愿意与她厮守一生，而这也真是这枚戒指的神圣使命所在。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">三</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">、登峰造极</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">如果你的女友是运动型，你可以在一天的攀岩活动之后，站在山峰的至高点向她求婚。其他可行的方法包括：跳伞时在半空中，潜水时在深海中，如此等等。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">四</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">、银幕为媒</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">你勉强同意陪她去看最新上映的超级言情大片。就在影片正式开演之前，播放了只有一行字幕的加片：</span>“xxx，你愿意做我的妻子吗?”虽然你不会因为精心导演此片而荣获奥斯卡奖，至少它会作为浪漫一幕被记录在该电影院的“院史”之中。<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（</span><a href=\"http://www.qiuhuning.com/\" target=\"_self\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 28px; white-space: normal;\">求婚总动员</a><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">.</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a href=\"http://www.qiuhuning.com/\" target=\"_self\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 28px; white-space: normal;\">求婚策划</a></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">部.浪漫策划师Rachel为您呈现）</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">五、录像表心意</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">制作一盘向她求婚的录像带很可以打动她的心，特别是如果你能够同她一起观看这盘录像。她一定会高兴得跳起来，立刻就要和你去度蜜月</span>……</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">六、空中</span>“要挟”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">一种更公开的方式是利用你们一起坐飞机的机会。你可以请求机长通过无线电通话系统将你的求婚传达给身边的女友。例如，你可以请机长说：</span>“我们正飞行在青藏高原的上空，再有将近40分钟就可以到达目的地。顺便说一句，安娜，李可问你他是否有幸能够娶你为妻。”在众目睽睽之下，相信你得到的只可能是一个“愿意”，当然，还有安全降落。</span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(219,21,0,'珠海万达上演浪漫求婚','','','Rachel',3,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2016-11-27 21:02:58','Rachel','','/upload/images/201611/14802518685515.jpg',1,1,'此刻我的心里依旧很激动，仿佛这一切都是梦，我现在依旧还在梦里，这一天我盼了很久，一直想给她一个浪漫的求婚...',0,'<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14802518685515.jpg\" title=\"珠海万达上演浪漫求婚.jpg\" alt=\"珠海万达上演浪漫求婚.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">他叫</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">魏洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，她叫</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">赵雪</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">魏洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">本是上海人，</span>6年前独自来到</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">珠海</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">打拼事业，工作非常的辛苦，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">时常很晚了还独自</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">一个人在公司</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">忙碌</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">工作，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">长时间作息不规律</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">让他半年的时间就</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">瘦</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">了</span>20斤，直到3年前他遇见</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">赵雪</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">这</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">个漂亮且善解人意的姑娘，也正因为</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">赵雪</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的出现使得他一个人在外地的生活可以过得更加的温暖幸福，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">赵雪</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">是</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">珠海</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">一个小镇上的姑娘，淳朴善良的她总会在休息的时间为</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">魏洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">学习炖各种好吃的汤给</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">魏洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">补身体，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">魏洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">总爱在吃饭时开玩笑说你把我都养成猪了。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14802519047327.jpg\" title=\"珠海万达上演浪漫求婚.jpg\" alt=\"珠海万达上演浪漫求婚.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">　　向</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">赵雪</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">魏洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">不只是想了一</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">两</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">次，三年里无数次求婚的想法在他脑海里浮现，而现在更</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">加坚定</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">了</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">这个想法</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，他请到</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚总动员</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">公司来帮忙策划这一场</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">浪漫</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚为的就是不那么平淡，他想这一场求婚可以使</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">赵雪</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">和自己的永远难忘</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">珠海</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">·</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">万达广场</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">我们的求婚进行得无比顺畅，显示屏里播放着他们的故事以及</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">魏洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的额表白视频，当</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">魏洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">从角落里走到</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">赵雪</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">面前时</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">赵雪</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">早已泣不成声，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚总动员</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划公司恭喜这一对即将踏入婚礼殿堂的他们永远幸福。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14802519446765.jpg\" title=\"珠海万达上演浪漫求婚.jpg\" alt=\"珠海万达上演浪漫求婚.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">成先生求婚感言：此刻我的心里依旧很激动，仿佛这一切都是梦，我现在依旧还在梦里，这一天我盼了很久，一直想给她一个浪漫的求婚，感谢</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚总动员</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划公司的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">精心</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">策划</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">与安排</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，祝愿全世界有情人终成眷属。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14802519756198.jpg\" title=\"珠海万达上演浪漫求婚.jpg\" alt=\"珠海万达上演浪漫求婚.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',100,375,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(220,21,0,'洛阳时代广场憨厚小伙真情告白','','','Rachel',3,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2016-11-27 21:37:10','Rachel','','/upload/images/201611/14802539483788.jpg',1,1,'今天我在这里向她求婚，来到我们第一次相遇的地方，感谢大家的支持与祝福...',0,'<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201611/14802539483788.jpg\" title=\"洛阳时代广场憨厚小伙真情告白.jpg\" alt=\"洛阳时代广场憨厚小伙真情告白.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><br/></span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">他叫</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刘洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，她叫</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，他们的恋爱路程特别的奇葩，因为</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">是他在路边</span>“拐”回家的</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">有</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">一次</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刘洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">晚上</span>1</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">1</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">点才下班，在路过</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">时代</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">广场时遇见了</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">这时已酩酊大醉的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">这时汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">非趴着</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刘洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">不要他走，而</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刘洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">想一个女生在外边不安全便把她带回了家，并拿出手机给她父母打了电话让她父母把她接了回去，在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的眼里</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刘洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">就是一个烂好人，这个世界上没有谁可以比他更傻了更好的人了，所以</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">死乞白赖</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的要和他在一起，开始</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刘洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">只把</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">当做是妹妹看待但是相处久了他也发现自己喜欢上了</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，在双方父母的同意之下他们在一起了</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">相处的两年里他们的爱情特别的戏剧，总爱发脾气的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">遇见了一个让她没法发脾气的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刘洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刘洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">在很多时候都宠着</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，这也让</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的脾气越来越蛮横，最终分手</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">而分开的两个人在没有了对方</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">独自一人生活</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">诸多</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">不适，两个月后两人又再度和好，和好后的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">脾气变得温顺了，他们的关系也更加的温馨融洽。</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">5年的恋爱时间他决心向她求婚给她一个惊喜，在</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚总动员</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划公司的帮助下，一场求婚即将在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">洛阳时代</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">广场展开</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">在</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">时代</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">广场，一条</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">1</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">0米宽的横幅引来诸多人的驻足观看，上边写着：“</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">汪蕊</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，嫁给我吧</span>!让我给你一辈子的幸福”</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">广场</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">中央</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">是由玫瑰</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">和蜡烛</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">摆成的</span>LOVE</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">以及</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">心形图案，女主在闺蜜的带领下来到我们的求婚现场，此时男主手捧</span>99朵玫瑰早已站在心形中间等着她的到来，在大家的热情助威下</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刘洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚成功。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">刘洋</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">在现场的求婚感言：</span>“6年前我第一次在这次遇见</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">酩酊大醉</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的馨儿，那个时候我不知道她就是我今生幸福，今天我在这里向她求婚，来到我们第一次相遇的地方，感谢大家的支持与祝福，感谢</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚总动员</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">公司的</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">精心策划与安排</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，我希望今后我和馨儿未来的日子可以永远像今天这么幸福开心，也祝愿大家永远幸福。</span>”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',97,1438,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(221,27,0,'10首为你的求婚完美助阵的歌曲','','','Rachel',3,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2016-11-27 21:42:06','Rachel','','',1,1,'i knew i loved you----澳洲组合savage garden的一首经典作品，不用多介绍了，有好朋友当年就是因为这首歌被她现在的老公追到的...',0,'<p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:28px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); let