e: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，又是说好话，又是包红包的，这才让死党们同意。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201612/14808304886335.png\" title=\"扬州催人泪下的求婚现场.png\" alt=\"扬州催人泪下的求婚现场.png\"/></p><p style=\";text-indent: 0;padding: 0;line-height: 24px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">他</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">和死党们约好九点整会与</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">女主</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">牵手一起来到大屏幕下，九点前，死党们早已</span>“埋伏“在附近，九点整，他们的身影出现在屏幕下，按计划屏幕上出现了</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">男主实现准备好的</span>MV</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，路人</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">们都说道</span>:</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">“屏幕上的人好温馨甜蜜呀，你看。。。。。。”放完后 “你愿意以后的日子跟我一切牵手走过吗?嫁给我!”当着众人的面</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">男主</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">单腿跪下，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">女主</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">被此情此景所感动。这时热烈的掌声响起，死党们从四面八方涌来，做这一刻永恒的见证。并预定好的鲜花及时送达，让幸福的她淹没在花的海洋，</span>999朵代表着爱的长长久久。而后屏幕上绽放烟花。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201612/14808305057133.png\" title=\"扬州催人泪下的求婚现场.png\" alt=\"扬州催人泪下的求婚现场.png\"/></p><p style=\";text-indent: 0;padding: 0;line-height: 24px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">　　然而，为了这场求婚，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">男主</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">可没少花功夫呢，请了我们</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: 