ont-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">今后</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的岁月，相信我</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">们</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">会</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">携手</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">一直走下去的</span>!”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:28px\"><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">“当然，也谢谢你们——</span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚总动员</span></span><strong><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划</span></span></strong><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">公司，做得很棒</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">哇咔咔。</span></span><span style=\";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px\">”</span></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',110,495,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(277,21,0,'珠海深情宅男沙滩求婚策划 动心女主感动落泪','','','qiuhuning',2,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','求婚策划,珠海求婚策划,室外求婚','深情宅男在老家珠海向女朋友求婚的故事',0,'2016-12-13 14:44:20','Addy','','/upload/images/201612/14816128434567.png',1,1,'想要问问我敢不敢，像对你承诺那样的爱你，12月8日晚上，我们一起在珠海飞沙滩见证了一场长达七年的恋爱，然后这场求婚更让小编明白了，这个世界上边最浪漫的三个字不是我爱你，而是在一起，这一份男女主都期待已久的求婚，从一开始准备那便是7年。下边小编便为大家讲解一下我们在珠海求婚策划的整个求婚故事。　　琪琪是一个端庄美丽的北京女孩，北方的环境和干燥让她向往着海边，小时候最渴望的便是在海边看日出日落，看那海',0,'<p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">想要问问我敢不敢，像对你承诺那样的爱你，</span>12月8<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">日晚上，我们一起在珠海飞沙滩见证了一场长达七年的恋爱，然后这场求婚更让小编明白了，这个世界上边最浪漫的三个字不是我爱你，而是在一起，这一份男女主都期待已久的求婚，从一开始准备那便是</span>7年。下边小编便为大家讲解一下<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">我们在</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 13px; text-decoration: none;\">珠海求婚策划</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 13px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">的整个求婚故事。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">琪</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">琪是一个端庄美丽的北京女孩，北方的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">环境和干燥让她</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">向往</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">着</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">海边，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">小时候最渴望的便是在海边看日出日落，看那海天一线的美景</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">顾远</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">从小便在海边长大</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">因为父母都是教师的原因，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">他的性格从小便</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">少</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">了些</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">活泼多了一丝沉稳，两人的爱情是</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">从</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">广州开始的，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">年双双考上广州中山大学的他们相遇在校园里边，因为选修课他们</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">在教师里</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">相识，沉稳的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">顾远</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">对</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">琪琪</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">一见钟情，因为</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">对彼此的印象都很好，所以</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">很快就在朋友的撮合下确定</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">了</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">恋情，相爱</span>1年</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">后</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的纪念日，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">顾远</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">带着</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">琪琪</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">回到自己的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">老</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">家</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">珠海</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，带她看了自己从小长大的城市以及海边，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">琪琪</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">最喜欢清早起床打开窗便</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">可以</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">看见海的那种美，而</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">顾远</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的家正好是</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">我们这次的</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚策划</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的场地</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">珠海的飞沙滩旁，从窗台往下看，可以看见海边的美景，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">此后的每逢</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">暑假寒假，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">琪琪</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">都喜欢往</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">顾远</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">家去玩，而</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">顾远</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的父母也很喜欢</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">琪琪</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">　　大学毕业后的他们</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">选择</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">回到的珠海生活，由于</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">顾远</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">是做编程这块的所以常常宅在家对着电脑，而身为银行专柜的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">琪琪</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">每天也是忙于工作，两人的爱情</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">虽然</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">平淡却也相处融洽。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">顾远</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">还</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">有一个爱好便是摄影，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">他</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">最喜欢拍的便是莫琪站在自家阳台上看大海的背影，至今在他的电脑中存储了至少上千张</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">琪琪</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的背影，他从拍第一张的时候就想着，这些背影是他对她最美的向往</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">是他们最美好的回忆</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">　　7年</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">在一起</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的时间早已使得两人的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的生活融入了彼此</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，一个眼神总是能够明白</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">对方</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">的想的是什么，所以两人之间总要一个人可以主动，那么，作为男人的他更是该主动。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:53px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">遇见爱，是</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">顾远这次沙滩</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">求婚</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">策划的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing