 style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">为她精心准备的求婚表白视频，看着现场的浪漫场景在蓝天与大海的相应下更加的美丽，她才知道，原来</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">顾远</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">为他做了这么多。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201612/14816126449636.png\" title=\"珠海深情宅男沙滩求婚策划 动心女主感动落泪.png\" alt=\"珠海深情宅男沙滩求婚策划 动心女主感动落泪.png\" style=\"\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:24px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 11px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">　　今夜的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">珠海</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">在我们的心中想必留下了不可磨灭的美，最幸福的瞬间是属于他们的夜晚，让我们祝福他们吧</span>!</span></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(298,27,0,'一场沙滩求婚策划方案','','','qiuhuning',2,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2016-12-19 14:52:24','Addy','','/upload/images/201612/14821305763998.png',1,1,'脚踏细沙，眼看大海！晨风照面，舒爽怡人；海味入鼻，直动心灵。白浪横接天地，卷卷而来，翻腾叠起，煞是有威。错落小岛，迫人遐想无穷；游艇飞梭，引动游人心绪，在水清沙幼的海滩上，许下一生挚爱的诺言，又会是何等的浪漫。下面跟随小编一起看看怎么策划一场浪漫的沙滩求婚吧！',0,'<p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">准备物品：</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">一，仪式亭</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1、</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">仪式亭：是由几个简单的架子构成，某宝上有卖的，搭配</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">纱幔</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">之后看着仪式感很浓厚。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px\">2、</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">仪式通道：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">由</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">鲜花铺出来的仪式亭通道，既清晰又浪漫</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 12px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">鲜花铺满仪式亭</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;marg