pan><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">你对她</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的爱，我相信</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">她</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">会明白，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">你会给她想要的依赖</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">让她</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">轻轻地闭上你的眼睛，把手交给</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">你</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，也把</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">她</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"fo