pan style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">地方等等，按照合适路线做好一天的安排。直到晚餐时间，就可以用提前组织好的求婚词以及求婚戒指向她求婚咯。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">意义独特的</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">定制餐具</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在你们的周年纪念日，买两个</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">定制的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">香槟</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">杯子和盘子</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，在杯子上刻上你们的名字和相识纪念日</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">日期</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，作为求婚定情物。你可以预先到所预定的餐馆，要求他们使用你提供的杯子。这会给你的伴侣很大的惊喜，也能成为你们俩结婚后很有意义的纪念品。好