INSERT INTO `archive` VALUES (361,21,0,'女孩对男生一见钟情 最终策划电影院求婚','','','qiuhuning',2,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2017-01-20 16:58:07','Addy','','/upload/images/201701/14849030130305.jpg',1,1,'既然遇见了，就不要错过。',0,'<p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">他们认识是在大学的广播站，她是负责招聘的人，第一天报名的时候，她就觉得男生长得很干净，就有些心动，报名结束之后通知男主角第二天来参加面试，但是第二天男主角并没有来，这可让女主角觉得是不是错过了什么，面试快结束的时候他来匆匆赶来，这时女主角才知道原来这世界上还真有一见钟情。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">他成功的争取到了在广播站工作的机会，男女主角彼此也就渐渐熟悉起来，都说女追男隔层纱，这次也不例外，男主角拜倒在女主角的石榴裙下。经过相处，两人发现他们之间的性格原来如此契合，不知不觉在一起的时间就过去了几年，毕业，工作后他们还是保持着最初遇见时那份心情。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0px;\">这次女主角终于下定决心求婚了，她找了专业的求婚策划公司，帮助她策划一场电影院的浪漫求婚</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">晚上，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">影厅已经开始播放影片，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">因为男主角的可以刻意实</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">没注意到</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的是</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，现场所有人的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">视线都在他们进来的时候转移过来</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">　　</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&nbsp; &nbsp;看电影的途中</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在专业求婚策划人员的打手势暗示后，女主角借口上厕所</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，离开了座位。几分钟后，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">大</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">银幕上的画面</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">戛然而止，播放的影片也换成了</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">两人</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">照片，随后</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">呈现的便是</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一幕幕两人恋爱时的故事画面，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">这让她</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">有些不知所错，但这才是刚刚开始。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">　　</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">现场</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，灯光亮起，女主角</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">从通道走出来</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，手捧鲜花，深情的注视着他说：</span>“你愿意娶我吗？”当女</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主角</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">问出这句话</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的同时</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，男</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">主角</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">终于也抑制不住内心的惊喜和感动，哽咽</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">着说</span>“我愿意”</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，两人在银幕下激动地拥吻在一起，随后亲朋们的祝福和尖叫声响彻现场</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">求婚策划公司的工作人员拍下了这样的照片</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">　　</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201701/14849027444156.png\" title=\"14849027444156.png\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" alt=\"14849027444156.png\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 400px;\"/></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(362,27,0,'川崎婚车队炸街','','','Rachel',3,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2017-01-20 21:23:08','Rachel','','',1,1,'显然你自己搞不定是吧,但是我们可以啊...',0,'<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;婚车，见多了也就见怪不怪了。就问一句川崎婚车队呼啸而过你怕不怕，回头率高不高，眼前一亮有没有？显然你自己搞不定是吧。但是我们可以啊。你想不到的，你搞不到的我们都可以啊。来啊 造作啊 反正有大把时光 ...<br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201701/14849193283400.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"川崎婚车队炸街.jpg\" alt=\"川崎婚车队炸街\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201701/14849193294653.png\" style=\"\" title=\"川崎婚车队炸街.jpg\" alt=\"川崎婚车队炸街\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201701/14849193319993.jpg\" style=\"\" title=\"川崎婚车队炸街.jpg\" alt=\"川崎婚车队炸街\"/></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(363,27,0,'This is 套路','','','Rachel',3,0,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2017-01-21 15:12:24','Rachel','','',1,1,'每一个女生都在期望着自己的求婚会是怎样的，而男生却在烦恼怎样的求婚才是最好的?可能你认