p:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">　　</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\">五</span>.进入最重要的求婚环节</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;line-height:22px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma\">　　一切的全部预备好了今后，带上你的女主角还有你的一颗诚心来到求婚现场，将你一切的预备工作淋漓尽致的发挥出来，让她感触到你精心预备的这场浪漫求婚之旅。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(408,21,0,'混血女生亲述被男友求婚过程','','','qiuhuning',2,1,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2017-02-22 18:11:07','Addy','','/upload/images/201702/14877594190978.jpg',1,1,'求婚策划都是老司机，让老司机教你开车，求婚妥妥的！',0,'<p style=\";text-indent: 0;padding: 0;line-height: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">他向我求婚</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的时候</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">，我们已经交往了</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">两</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">年。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">我</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">一直都</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">相信可以找到一个心灵契合的人，而我们最初约会的时候我知道我已经找到了。由最初相识我知道他是我要找的人，那是一个真正了解我，能够走进我心扉，以及我感觉到连系的人。我们的一个共同朋友在派对让我们互相认识，他问我一起出去约会，自从那次之后，我们就没有分开过了！他选择了最完美的方式向我求婚！他请了求婚策划师在场地做准备。他知道我喜欢花，也经常送花给我，所以在这个特别的日子，策划师就建议他在我们的房子放满了花朵，令整个地方都荡漾着浪漫的氛围，不单止这样</span>...</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201702/14877582862449.jpg\" title=\"14877582862449.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">当我们走进的时候，那个场境真的让我很惊艳：</span> <span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">四处都布满了鲜花还有蜡烛，柔软的白色布幕挂着闪亮的星星灯泡</span>...犹如进入了一个童话故事中！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201702/14877582924735.jpg\" title=\"14877582924735.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">他带我到沙发坐下，然后我发现了一个闪闪的</span>MARRY ME的字形木牌... 他就跪下，问我可不可以嫁给他！我非常惊喜的！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201702/14877582998270.jpg\" title=\"14877582998270.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">之后，他开了香槟，我们躺下享受这个奇妙的氛围</span>... 我在人生中从未感受到这么开心！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201702/14877583067572.jpg\" title=\"14877583067572.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">但这个惊喜还未结束，因为他要求了求婚策划师请来一位专业厨师，准备好餐桌。厨师为我们预备了一顿精彩的欧式晚餐，为这完美的一晚划上完美的结尾！</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-align:center;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: baskerville;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201702/14877583111436.jpg\" title=\"14877583111436.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p><br/></p>','0','','0','',0,0,'','','','求婚总动员',0,'','',0,'N;','',0,0,0,'0000-00-00','','','','','','','','','','','','',0,'',1,'',0),(409,21,0,'在香港维多利亚港求婚','','','qiuhuning',2,1,'',0,0,'',0,'','','','',0,'2017-02-23 17:35:34','Addy','','/upload/images/201702/14878427044142.jpg',1,1,'人生不止是诗和酒，还有爱人和家庭。',0,'<p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">陈琳颖</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">和我在求婚之前已经有一段时间在谈及和计划结婚的事。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">因为我俩</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">那时候</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">都很忙，所以我相信她绝对意想不到会有这个求婚惊喜</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">！</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201702/14878425731425.jpg\" title=\"14878425731425.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">所以，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">当</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">我负责计划我们的周年纪念日</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">的时候</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">，我</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">觉得</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">可以趁这个机会借口说要带她共进一顿浪漫的晚餐。当我们离开餐厅之后，我们就前往维多利亚港海旁，那里有美丽动人的城市</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">夜</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">景。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">在哪里我的策划师早已准备好了一切。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: times;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">当晚的天气不太好，整天都下着大雨，我们刚到达的时候又开始下雨了！我很担心所有的计划都要落空</span>...幸好，我们等了十分钟后，雨又停了。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201702/14878425911465.jpg\" title=\"14878425911465.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">其实这场雨也令这件事变得更特别，雨水把墙壁都擦得闪亮，反射着所有的光，不单止美丽的香港天际线，还有求婚策划师准备的烛光和小灯泡。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201702/14878426069471.jpg\" title=\"14878426069471.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">当我们走上前的时候，</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">她</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">察觉到这一切都是为她准备的。她看到我在黑板上写的字：</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">“</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">周年快乐！爱你的</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">熊敬</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">上。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">”</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">然后她开始哭了，我拿着一束红玫瑰和戒指，在她面前跪下。她非常感动！</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/upload/images/201702/14878426162821.jpg\" title=\"14878426162821.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\">&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:21px;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">我们永远都不会忘记这一刻。一会儿我们发现一位摄影师在拍我们（我其实早已知道，但因为太感动忘记了），所以</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">关于</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Book Antiqua&#39;;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Book Antiqua\">我们</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(25, 25, 25);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13